# CSS and Styling Guidelines

## Tailwind CSS Architecture

### Configuration ([tailwind.config.js](mdc:tailwind.config.js))

- Content paths: `["./src/**/*.{html,md,njk,js}"]`
- Custom stone color palette (stone-50 through stone-900)
- Custom fonts: Georgia serif, Inter sans-serif

### Source CSS ([src/css/styles.css](mdc:src/css/styles.css))

Uses Tailwind layers and `@apply` directives:

```css
@tailwind base;
@tailwind components;
@tailwind utilities;
```

### Custom Components

- `.btn` - Base button styling with transitions
- `.btn-primary` - Primary stone-700 background
- `.btn-secondary` - Secondary stone-200 background
- `.card` - White background with border and shadow
- `.grave-card` - Card with hover effects
- `.gallery-grid` - Responsive image grid
- `.masonry-item` - Gallery image containers

## Color Scheme

Stone palette throughout:

- **Backgrounds**: stone-50 (light), stone-800 (dark headers)
- **Text**: stone-800 (primary), stone-600 (secondary), stone-400 (tertiary)
- **Borders**: stone-200, stone-300
- **Hover states**: stone-200, stone-900

## Build Process

- **Source**: [src/css/styles.css](mdc:src/css/styles.css) with Tailwind directives
- **Output**: `_site/css/styles.css` with compiled CSS
- **Watch**: `npm run css:watch` for development
- **Build**: `npm run css:build` for production

## Responsive Design

- Mobile-first approach with `md:` and `lg:` breakpoints
- Grid layouts: `grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3`
- Container max-width with `container mx-auto px-4`

## Common Patterns

- Navigation: `bg-stone-800 text-white hover:text-stone-200`
- Cards: `bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6 border border-stone-200`
- Buttons: `px-4 py-2 rounded-md font-medium transition-colors`
- Images: `w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-md`
